  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, multi-center, open-label, PK and safety profile study of enteral
      digoxin in children &lt;6 months old at time of enrollment, post-surgical or hybrid stage 1
      palliation, but prior to surgical stage 2 palliation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
